#: addons/economy_modifier.wad/addon:2 input:7 standard
msgid "Economy Modifier Addon"
msgstr "Weertskupp-Ännerns-Verwiedern"

#: addons/economy_modifier.wad/addon:3 input:6 standard
msgid ""
"This mod changes the production logic so that buildings only create wares or "
"workers if they are required. Each ware has a predefined target value, which "
"can still be modified during gameplay."
msgstr ""
"Deeses Ännern ännert de Produzerens-Logik so, dat Husen blots Waren of "
"Arbeiders produzeren, wenn se bruukt worden. Elkeen Waar hett eene vörgeven "
"Enn-Tahl, wat wiederhen im Speel anpasst worden kann."

